name: FarmerDoge
description: FarmerDoge is the first multi-dividend rewards token setout to feed the world.Founded on August 20th, 2021, FarmerDoge was created to make holding onto your tokens easier by rewarding holders with rewards in any coin on the BSC network, and any Binance-Pegged tokens.The company wants to move into the charity realm and real world utility of providing food to those less fortunate.The company plans on partnering with local farmers around the world to get donated/buy imperfect foods deemed unfit for supermarkets They would then bringing them to partnered restaurants to have fresh meals prepared to handout to those in need , and to bring to homeless shelters within the community.
